sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Client (admin)
    participant Ctl as OrdersController
    participant Svc as Doc / Actions services
    participant M as Mailer / Doc store / Session
    C->>Ctl: GET agreement.pdf|.docx  (orders.agreement.read)
    Ctl->>Svc: streamAgreement(id, format)
    Svc-->>C: 200 StreamableFile
    C->>Ctl: POST invite-user / resend-* (throttled)
    Ctl->>Svc: OrderActionsService
    Svc->>M: send one email (reject if inside throttle)
    Svc-->>C: 200/201
    C->>Ctl: POST :id/impersonate
    Ctl->>Svc: mint exhibitor session
    Svc-->>C: 200 + Set-Cookie SBEEXHIBITOR_* (+ audit)
